2011-03-25T16:15:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-25/aquarius-says-zimbabwe-wants-miners-response-on-local-ownership-law.html
(Corrects spelling of  Zimbabwe  in headline.)  Aquarius Platinum Ltd. (AQP)  said the
Zimbabwean mines minister has gazetted a notice demanding to
know within 45 days how mining companies will meet local
ownership targets.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
